io.github.rubenchristoffer.hetty.html

Class HTMLDocumentWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.rubenchristoffer.hetty.html.HTMLNodeWrapper
      • io.github.rubenchristoffer.hetty.html.HTMLDocumentWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<HTMLNodeWrapper>, Document, Node

    public class HTMLDocumentWrapper
extends HTMLNodeWrapper
implements Document
    Class that acts as a wrapper for a HTML Document. This means that all methods are being handled by the underlying Document interface (this class doesn't actually implement any interface methods itself). It also contains a few additional helper functions that are not part of the interface.
    Author:
    Ruben Christoffer
